:?}\", foo);\n}\n\nfn main() {\n    // Calling the method is still fine, as i32 implements Debug.\n    some_func(5i32);\n\n    // This would fail to compile now:\n    // struct WithoutDebug;\n    // some_func(WithoutDebug);\n}\n```\n\nRust only looks at the signature of the called function, as such it must\nalready specify all requirements that will be used for every type parameter.\n"},"level":"error","spans":[{"file_name":"src/quic_server.rs","byte_start":4681,"byte_end":4694,"line_start":139,"line_end":139,"column_start":9,"column_end":22,"is_primary":true,"text":[{"text":"        quinn::VarInt::from(quic_config.idle_timeout * 1000).into()","highlight_start":9,"highlight_end":22}],"label":"the trait `From<u64>` is not implemented for `VarInt`","suggested_replacement":null,"suggestion_applicability":null,"expansion":null}],"children":[{"message":"the following other types implement trait `From<T>`:\n  `VarInt` implements `From<h3_quinn::quinn::StreamId>`\n  `VarInt` implements `From<u16>`\n  `VarInt` implements `From<u32>`\n  `VarInt` implements `From<u8>`","code":null,"level":"help","spans":[],"children":[],"rendered":null}],"rendered":"\u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;9merror[E0277]\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\u001b[1m: the trait bound `VarInt: From<u64>` is not satisfied\u001b[0m\n\u001b[0m   \u001b[0m\u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;12m--> \u001b[0m\u001b[0msrc/quic_server.rs:139:9\u001b[0m\n\u001b[0m    \u001b[0m\u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;12m|\u001b[0m\n\u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;12m139\u001b[0m\u001b[0m \u001b[0m\u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;12m|\u001b[0m\u001b[0m \u001b[0m\u001b[0m        quinn::VarInt::from(quic_config.idle_timeout * 1000).into()\u001b[0m\n\u001b[0m    \u001b[0m\u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;12m|\u001b[0m\u001b[0m         \u001b[0m\u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;9m^^^^^^^^^^^^^\u001b[0m\u001b[0m \u001b[0m\u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;9mthe trait `From<u64>` is not implemented for `VarInt`\u001b[0m\n\u001b[0m    \u001b[0m\u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;12